The paper introduces a deep generative autoencoder with autoregressive connections, which is a popular approach in the field of deep learning. The paper also discusses an efficient parameter estimation method based on the minimum description length (MDL) principle, which is a common technique in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
